                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr />
        </div>
        <div class="copyright">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-6 text-center text-lg-left">
                        <div class="copyright-content">
                            <p><a href="https://www.templateshub.net">Cinemang | 2021</a> Tüm Hakları Saklıdır.      (DEUCENG)</p>
                        </div>
